de names is measured using", "bbox": [177.9, 1027.2, 1142.8, 1055.3]}, {"text": "the relief-from-royalty method. This method assumes the trade name has value to the extent that the owner is", "bbox": [177.9, 1052.2, 1142.6, 1080.3]}, {"text": "relieved of the obligation to pay royalties for the benefits received from them. This method requires us to estimate", "bbox": [177.9, 1077.2, 1142.8, 1105.3]}, {"text": "the future revenue for the related brands, the appropriate royalty rate and the weighted average cost of capital.", "bbox": [177.9, 1102.2, 1102.1, 1130.3]}, {"text": "12.", "bbox": [100.5, 1151.9, 132.1, 1180.7]}, {"text": "Income Taxes", "bbox": [171.4, 1151.9, 293.6, 1180.7]}, {"text": "Income from continuing operations before income taxes consisted of the following:", "bbox": [100.5, 1177.2, 802.2, 1205.3]}, {"text": "Years ended December 31", "bbox": [859.4, 1217.8, 1090.4, 1246.6]}, {"text": "In millions", "bbox": [106.7, 1244.7, 196.5, 1272.5]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [840.8, 1244.1, 881.0, 1272.9]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [954.7, 1244.1, 995.2, 1272.9]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [1068.4, 1244.1, 1109.4, 1272.9]}, {"text": "Federal (1)", "bbox": [106.7, 1270.6, 187.9, 1298.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [819.7, 1270.7, 830.1, 1298.7]}, {"text": "(32.8)", "bbox": [851.7, 1270.7, 903.1, 1298.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [933.7, 1270.7, 944.1, 1298.7]}, {"text": "(25.6)", "bbox": [965.7, 1270.7, 1017.1, 1298.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1047.7, 1270.7, 1058.1, 1298.7]}, {"text": "(21.8)", "bbox": [1079.7, 1270.7, 1131.1, 1298.7]}, {"text": "International (2)", "bbox": [106.7, 1296.9, 234.7, 1325.0]}, {"text": "522.0", "bbox": [848.2, 1296.9, 895.1, 1325.0]}, {"text": "586.6", "bbox": [962.2, 1296.9, 1009.1, 1325.0]}, {"text": "534.3", "bbox": [1076.2, 1296.9, 1123.1, 1325.0]}, {"text": "Income from continuing operations before income taxes", "bbox": [106.7, 1323.2, 579.8, 1351.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [819.7, 1323.2, 830.1, 1351.2]}, {"text": "489.2", "bbo